Subject:[CT Birds] some advice on chasing hurricane birds
Not sure if the BirdingNews translator will mess up the zeros and letter
O's in the following internet URL, but here is some interesting 1998!
advice (from North Carolina) for chasing hurricane birds -- much of it is
still pertinent, although it focuses too much on the eye of a storm:

http://www.ibiblio.org/pardo/birds/archive/archive2/msg00058.html

